3 (ii) all golf courses, including land and improvements actually and necessarily used for that
4 purpose, that consist of at least nine holes and not less than 700 lineal yards;
5 (iii) commercial buildings and parcels of land upon which the buildings are situated;
6 (iv) shooting ranges THAT ARE NOT EXEMPT FROM PROPERTY TAXES UNDER 15-6-201 AND ARE operated
7 by an entity that is a nonprofit corporation exempt from taxation under 26 U.S.C. 501(c)(3) or 501(c)(4) of the
